      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Punctuation</strong> -  Field 508 ends with a period unless another mark of punctuation is present.
      </div>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Display Constant</strong> -  Introductory term <em>Credits:</em> that often appears with the data recorded in field
                     508 is not carried in the MARC record. It may be system generated as a display constant
                     associated with the field tag.
      </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>CONTENT DESIGNATOR HISTORY</h3>
      <div class="font_small">In 2001, the field was changed from Not-repeatable (NR) to Repeatable (R) to record
   complex or multiple credit notes.</div>
